<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٩٨٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">قُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4085">عَبْدُ الْوَهَّابِ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/857">أَيُّوبُ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3667">أَبِي قِلَابَةَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كُنْتُ رَدِيفَ أَبِي طَلْحَةَ وَإِنَّهُمْ لَيَصْرُخُونَ بِهِمَا جَمِيعًا: الْحَجِّ وَالْعُمْرَةِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>